title: Legacy Games - Pretty In Pink - New HOG - Wendy99
description:
Pretty in Pink  


The classic 80s hit movie, Pretty in Pink, is known as a movie that defined a generation, and now players will have the chance to relive the memorable story about love, friendship and the clash of social cliques in an entertaining game format.


System Requirements:

Windows XP/Vista 1 GHz or faster CPU 512 MR RAM DirectX 7.0 or later 16-bit Sound Card
